OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FCloudier on Wednesday with some rain
OL,7,Flikely. Thursday and Friday, mostly
OL,8,Fdry with bright or sunny spells.
OL,9,FTurning very warm, perhaps locally
OL,10,Fhot, and feeling increasingly humid.
OL,11,FThundery showers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
